  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "KBP VSK-94 9x39步枪",
      "en": "KBP VSK-94 9x39 rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "VSK-94",
      "en": "VSK-94"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 52,354₽ | 物品价值: 19,370 | Mechanic报价: 10,847₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 55,230₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级1 < GP x15 | Σ ≈ 112,500₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级2 < 54,181₽\n\nVSK-94（俄语“军用狙击装备 94 型”的缩写）是一款基于 9A-91 突击步枪设计的特种狙击步枪，其定位为 VSS 的廉价平替。与VSS不同的是，它的消音器并非一体安装，可以在不需要时卸下。由 KBP 机械设计局研发，图拉兵工厂制造。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 52,354₽ | 物品价值: 19,370 | Mechanic报价: 10,847₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 55,230₽\n购买渠道 @ 竞技场裁判 等级1 < GP x15 | Σ ≈ 112,500₽\n购买渠道 @ Prapor 等级2 < 54,181₽\n\nThe VSK-94 (Voyskovoy Snayperskiy Kompleks - \"Military Sniper Complex\") is a marksman rifle designed on the base of the 9A-91 assault rifle as a cheaper alternative to the VSS \"Vintorez\". The silencer, unlike the VSS, is not integrated, which allows the rifle to be used without it if needed. Manufactured by Tula KBP Instrument Design Bureau."
    },
